channel.title: Cache extractor error
channel.description:
does any one know what the problem is, i've tried defyboys. I found a pre 317 cache on my old computer, , its about a year and a half after beta. and 6 months before 317. and waas wondering what this error was:
Exporting New Cache Files.
Runescape Cache Exporter 3.0 -/- (C) 2008 Troy Osborne (defyboy) -/- -------------------------------- The sprite extracter thingy was by Miss Silabsoft (EWW) -------------------------------- Things added in This Version: Fixed Some of the broken rules A Easier Names parser Sprite Dumper (old Engine Cache) -------------------------------- Parsing Rules... - 5 Caches Loaded. Extracting Cache Files... - Extracting Expected 9 in Cache 0 "gamedata"... PANIC! RANDOMISED BLOCK! Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 18002 at cacheexport2.PackJAG.method68(PackJAG.java:133) at cacheexport2.PackJAG.method73(PackJAG.java:584) at cacheexport2.JagFile.loadstream(JagFile.java:28) at cacheexport2.JagFile.<init>(JagFile.java:17) at cacheexport2.Unpack.Unpack1(Unpack.java:48) at cacheexport2.Main.ExtractCacheFiles(Main.java:64) at cacheexport2.Main.main(Main.java:39)
